# TileOverlayErrorEvent

**Class**

An event object that notifies the developer of an error that occurred while loading tiles.

## Declaration

```swift
class TileOverlayErrorEvent extends MapKitEvent
```

## Discussion

[doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/TileOverlay] dispatches a `tile-error` event when an error occurs while loading tiles.

## Instance Properties

- **tileOverlay**: The tile overlay object that dispatched the tile error event.
- **tileUrl**: The URL of the tile that failed to load.

## Inherits From

- MapKitEvent
